Package com.facebook.buck.core.model.platform.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConstraintBasedPlatform
    An implementation of a Platform that has a fixed set of constraints.
    CpuConstraintDetector
    A constraint detector that matches the constraint value to the host CPU.
    DefaultPlatform
    A platform that fails when constraints are checked.
    EmptyPlatform
    A platform that doesn't match any constraints.
    OsConstraintDetector
    A constraint detector that matches the constraint value to the host OS name.
    ThrowingPlatformResolver
    Platform resolver which always throws.
